    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine, showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously maintained since day one. Finished in a stunning deep metallic paint that has been protected by a professional ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed only. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear or bolster creasing, the carpets are spotless, and it has never been smoked in. Mechanically, this car is perfect. It comes with a comprehensive, documented service history from the authorized dealership, including a recent major inspection and a fresh set of premium tires. Every feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist technology, functions exactly as intended. This vehicle includes both original keys, all owner's manuals, and original factory floor mats. If you are looking for a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a new model, this is the one.",
      "price": 44900.0,
